OL,6,FA #20 million bid to buy more than 100
OL,7,Facres of land in Sark has been
OL,8,Frejected.
OL,10,FSark Property Company Ltd. submitted a
OL,11,Fcash bid in October to purchase around
OL,12,F80 residential dwellings and 20
OL,13,Fcommercial properties from the estate
OL,14,Fof the late Sir David Barclay.
OL,16,FThe company, set up in 2023 by 23rd
OL,17,FSeigneur of Sark Christopher Beaumont
OL,18,Fand entrepreneur Swen Lorenz,
OL,19,Fsubmitted a #20 million cash bid to
OL,20,Fbuy 20% of Sark's real estate.
