OL,6,FThe purchase hoped to "transform the
OL,7,Fisland" by fixing Sark's housing
OL,8,Fshortages, financial challenges, and
OL,9,Finsufficient facilities following the
OL,10,Fclosure of several hospitality outlets.
OL,12,FHowever, the property company now say
OL,13,Fthe bid has failed as Barclay estate
OL,14,Fwanted a higher asking price.
OL,16,FThey added the rejected bid was "not
OL,17,Fwhat (they) hoped for".
