OL,3,CCash bid to purchase 20% of Sark's
OL,4,Creal estate rejected
OL,6,FSwen Lorenz, CEO of Sark Property
OL,7,FCompany Ltd, said: "Our offer of #20
OL,8,Fmillion was, we believe, a fair
OL,9,Freflection of the portfolio's value
OL,10,Fwith a small premium on top.
OL,12,F"We worked closely with our advisor
OL,13,FSavills Guernsey to calculate what the
OL,14,Festate is worth, considering its
OL,15,Fcurrent condition and wider factors
OL,16,Flike the challenging tourism situation
OL,17,Ffor the whole of the Bailiwick.
OL,19,F"However, the asking price of the
OL,20,Fcurrent owner was so much higher that
OL,21,Fthere was no way to bridge the gap."
