OL,3,CCash bid to purchase 20% of Sark's
OL,4,Creal estate rejected
OL,6,FThe Sark Property Company has also
OL,7,Fannounced that in light of the
OL,8,Fdecision, the board will wind down its
OL,9,Factivities but may revisit the
OL,10,Fsituation in 2026.
OL,12,FSeigneur of Sark Christopher Beaumont
OL,13,Fsaid: "The trustees who are in charge
OL,14,Fof this portfolio have said that they
OL,15,Fare going to further develop the
OL,16,Festate and this is a pledge that Sark
OL,17,Fdesperately needs to see fulfilled.
