OL,6,FLater speaking to ITV News, the
OL,7,FSeigneur spoke of how he was anxious
OL,8,Fthe plans put forward by the Barclay's
OL,9,Fto redevelop the island may not come
OL,10,Fto pass.
OL,12,FHe said: "I'm slightly concerned that
OL,13,Fthe plan won't come to fruition but
OL,14,Ftime will we shall see. Time will
OL,15,Ftell."
OL,17,F"I, and many other Sark residents,
OL,18,Flook forward to hearing the plan and
OL,19,Fseeing the trustees make overdue
OL,20,Fimprovements to their estate."
